---
import Base from '../../layouts/Base.astro';
---
<Base title="About · Latest AI News">
  <section class="hero">
    <h1>About</h1>
    <p>Latest AI News is a lightweight source-linked AI intelligence site focused on executives, founders, podcasts, YouTube, X, top media, official blogs, labs, investors and developer ecosystems.</p>
  </section>
  <section class="card">
    <h2>Principles</h2>
    <p>No fake links, no paywall bypass, no full-text copying, no test data in production. Every item must carry an original source URL, category, date, source name and concise bilingual summary.</p>
    <h2>Schedule</h2>
    <p>The daily workflow runs at 23:12 UTC, equal to 07:12 Beijing/Taipei time.</p>
    <h2>How to submit a source</h2>
    <p>Add source metadata to the registry, prefer official RSS or podcast RSS, and run the validation scripts before publishing.</p>
  </section>
</Base>
